text: George Elsden (born c. 1530), of Lyme Regis, Dorset, was an English politician. He was a Member (MP) of the Parliament of England for Reigate in 1558 and for Lyme Regis in 1572. ==References== Category:1530 births Category:Year of death missing Category:People from Lyme Regis Category:English MPs 1558 Category:English MPs 1572–1583
